        >
          Role-Based Access
          <br />
          <span class="text-text-muted">Secure Team Permissions</span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto"
        >
          Granular permissions for Owner, Admin, Manager, Staff, and Viewer
          roles. Control what each team member can view, edit, and manage.
        </p>

        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-12">
          <a
