            <h3 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-4">
              Enterprise Permission System
            </h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
              Role-based access control integrates with single sign-on providers
              to automatically assign permissions based on identity provider
              attributes. When employees authenticate through SSO systems,
              CalendHub maps organizational role and department to appropriate
              permission levels automatically. This eliminates manual permission
              configuration for new team members while ensuring consistent
              security policies. Permission changes propagate instantly without
              requiring logout. Audit logs capture every permission change with
              timestamp, user, and modification details for compliance
              requirements. These logs remain immutable and export for security
              analysis or compliance reporting to meet regulatory requirements
              in healthcare, finance, and regulated industries.
            </p>
